  <text xml:base="urn:cts:latty:scientia01.latty2701538latty-lat1" xml:lang="lat">
    <body n="body1">
      <div n="div1">
        <head n="head1">Panegyrica ode quam illustrissimo et reverendissimo domino domino<persName n="persName1">Carolo Madrutio</persName>
          <placeName n="placeName2">Tridenti</placeName>episcopo consecrato accinebat<persName n="persName3">J.B. Scientia</persName>.</head>
        <p n="p2">
          <placeName n="placeName1">Tridenti</placeName>, apud<persName n="persName2">Iohannem Albertum</persName>.<date n="date3">MDCXXVI</date>.</p>
        <p n="p3">Superiorum Permissu.<pb n="pb1"/>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div n="div2">
        <head n="head1">Tricolos pentastrophos.</head>
        <lg n="lg2">
          <lg n="lg1" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Felix o superum munere civitas,</l>
            <l n="l2">O felix iterum, cui Deus altior</l>
            <l n="l3">Fortuna dominus praeficit, et suo</l>
            <l n="l4">Decretum fato</l>
            <l n="l5">Vult imperare<persName n="persName1">CAROLUM</persName>.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg2" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Non illo pietas, et meritis satis</l>
            <l n="l2">Virtus facta suis, quae vetat emori</l>
            <l n="l3">Iam functos homines: non amor, et boni</l>
            <l n="l4">Communis cura</l>
            <l n="l5">Possunt abesse, sospite.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg3" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Pendet crimina, grex perstrepat ilicet,</l>
            <l n="l2">Aequum iustitiae, Pricipe dignior</l>
            <l n="l3">Virtus, rara tamen, sed tamen omnibus</l>
            <l n="l4">Omni sub saeclo,</l>
            <l n="l5">Virtutibus sublimior.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg4" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Sive urbem deceat quis decor, adferet,</l>
            <l n="l2">Seu civem status: usquam mala (sedulus</l>
            <l n="l3">Aeternis vicibus in bona subditi)</l>
            <l n="l4">Admittet nunquam,</l>
            <l n="l5">Regnare doctus a suis.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg5" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Dic o dic patria, cui domino mage</l>
            <l n="l2">Optasti eximio vivere sub iugo?</l>
            <l n="l3">Non sic Romuleo nomine septimons</l>
            <l n="l4">Plebes Romana</l>
            <l n="l5">Digne superbiat modo.</l>
          </lg>
          <pb n="pb6"/>
          <lg n="lg7" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Non Spartana suis, Graecia non suis,</l>
            <l n="l2">Non digne Priamo gaudeat Ilion,</l>
            <l n="l3">Nec Thebe Hercule, nec Persia nobilis</l>
            <l n="l4">Legislatore,</l>
            <l n="l5">Se nulla praeferat tibi;</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg8" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Cui MADRUTIA reddit Domus arbitra</l>
            <l n="l2">Sub miti imperio iura, sibi et suis</l>
            <l n="l3">Vel solo hoc similis: credite posteri,</l>
            <l n="l4">Se virtus laudat</l>
            <l n="l5">Legata norma posteris.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg9" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Hanc qui Nile caput contegis, Ister hanc,</l>
            <l n="l2">Et Tigris rapidus suspicitis domum:</l>
            <l n="l3">Hanc ipse Oceanus dissitus, ultimo,</l>
            <l n="l4">Exornamentum</l>
            <l n="l5">Europae inaudit Hespero.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg10" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Huis venit meritis gloria quaelibet</l>
            <l n="l2">Par nunquam: titulus insuper inclitus,</l>
            <l n="l3">Subiectorum animis addere fortius</l>
            <l n="l4">Ad mores calcar,</l>
            <l n="l5">Ad recta, ad aequa pergere.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg11" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Ut possint placidis lumina condere</l>
            <l n="l2">In somnis alii, sic vigilabitur</l>
            <l n="l3">Tanto a Principe. Non vixeris ancium</l>
            <l n="l4">Rerum Tridentum,</l>
            <l n="l5">Est qui pericla submovet.</l>
          </lg>
          <pb n="pb12"/>
          <lg n="lg13" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Erranti iniiciet frena licentiae,</l>
            <l n="l2">Artes ut veteres inuehat, a quibus</l>
            <l n="l3">Augetur decus, et crescit honor suo</l>
            <l n="l4">Porrectus cursu</l>
            <l n="l5">Qua nascitur caditque sol.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg14" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Virtus his animo crescit, et amplior</l>
            <l n="l2">Ad summum decus extenditur his via,</l>
            <l n="l3">Formavere rudes protinus insciam</l>
            <l n="l4">His anni mentem,</l>
            <l n="l5">Grassatur his ad gloriam.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg15" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Quis nunc egregio sub domino timens</l>
            <l n="l2">Credit fervitium? Fallitur: alterum</l>
            <l n="l3">Non est praesidium tutius aprius</l>
            <l n="l4">Nostro, cui praesto</l>
            <l n="l5">Iustus piusque CAROLUS.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg16" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Quo custode, furor civicus, exterus</l>
            <l n="l2">Nullis temporibus conteret otium,</l>
            <l n="l3">Nec quae sic gladios ira acuit truces,</l>
            <l n="l4">Urbes ut cive,</l>
            <l n="l5">Civesque privet urbibus.</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg17" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Hospes Thrax etiamsi foret, aut novo</l>
            <l n="l2">Ex orbe adveniens Cantaber, annuet</l>
            <l n="l3">Laudatum Patriae promerito patris</l>
            <l n="l4">Nomen; dicetque:</l>
            <l n="l5">Sic civitas beata fit.</l>
          </lg>
          <pb n="pb18"/>
          <lg n="lg19" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Quorsum Musa? Tuo non opus his sono</l>
            <l n="l2">Quae sunt clara suo: laudibus abstine.</l>
            <l n="l3">Queis per digna labor facta mererier</l>
            <l n="l4">Laudes, cur curent</l>
            <l n="l5">Audire laudis omnia?</l>
          </lg>
          <lg n="lg20" type="stanza">
            <l n="l1">Ergo dum propriis fontibus invicem</l>
            <l n="l2">Distabunt Athesis, Cydnus, et Albula,</l>
            <l n="l3">Vivat MADRUTIO sanguine nobilis</l>
            <l n="l4">Aeternum aeternum</l>
            <l n="l5">Orbi precemur ut Domus.</l>
          </lg>
        </lg>
      </div>
      <div n="div3">
        <head n="head1">Tradita illustrissimo et reverendissimo domino domino Carolo Madrutio Episcopatus
                insignia</head>
        <lg n="lg2">
          <l n="l1">In pennas allapsa suas cur Fama sereno</l>
          <l n="l2">Aethere devehitur? Fallor, an ipsa Dea est?</l>
          <l n="l3">Laeta Tridentinus per compita fertur ovanti</l>
          <l n="l4">Nereus adsimilis: stat sine nube polus.</l>
          <l n="l5">Insolito micat orbe dies nitidissima: quid si</l>
          <l n="l6">Prisca novis revebat saecula Phoebus equis?</l>
          <l n="l7">Ah revehet, non ille quidem qui temperat annum,</l>
          <l n="l8">Sed qui sacra novo nomine frena regit.</l>
          <l n="l9">Ecce manu Mitram praetedens Fama, superni</l>
          <l n="l10">Doni tibi Mitram, sic tulit orsa, Iovis.</l>
          <pb n="pb11"/>
          <l n="l12">O quonda-<emph n="emph1">M AD RUTI</emph>-lum trino diademate peplum</l>
          <l n="l13">Quem genus, et pietas, quem tua fata vocant:</l>
          <l n="l14">Accipe nunc certo maioribus omine nomen</l>
          <l n="l15">Fascibus auspicium, dignior ipse datis:</l>
          <l n="l16">Post meriti venient fasces. Tanto incipe, pondus</l>
          <l n="l17">Assuetis humeris ne grave Mundus eat.</l>
          <l n="l18">Intonuit faustum Deus his, votoque frequenti</l>
          <l n="l19">Emeritae imposita est Insula sacra comae.</l>
          <l n="l20">Aeternos sperare potes tibi frontis honores;</l>
          <l n="l21">Si tibi quae data sunt, sunt data teste Deo.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
      <div n="div4">
        <head n="head1">Idem illustrissimus et reverendissimus CAROLUS EPISCOPUS</head>
        <head n="head2">Per anagramma.</head>
        <head n="head3">SIC POPULO CARUS ES</head>
        <lg n="lg4">
          <l n="l1">Iam lugent inhorora suum decus arva pruinis</l>
          <l n="l2">Iam nemus albescit, iam iuga cana rigent.</l>
          <l n="l3">Nec nemoris luctum, nec supputat arva Tridentum</l>
          <l n="l4">Veris dissimiles explicuisse comas.</l>
          <l n="l5">Vere novo gaudens petit undique et undique; festos</l>
          <l n="l6">Quo celebres sacro signet honore dies.</l>
          <pb n="pb7"/>
          <l n="l8">Sed quid Io? Cessit ne alii sua iura Bootes</l>
          <l n="l9">Hinc ne Tridentini gaudia tanta fori?</l>
          <l n="l10">Tempora nimirum te Praeside dura recedunt,</l>
          <l n="l11">Carole,<emph n="emph1">SIC POPULO CARUS ES</emph>, ille tibi.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
      <div n="div5">
        <head n="head1">Anni praelagium.
            Quo illustrissimus et reverendissimus Carolus Madrucius 
            Episcopus est renunciandus.
